ziegfeld girl is a 1941 american musical comedy film directed by robert z. leonard and starring william powell , judy garland , and lana turner . it was directed by robert z. leonard and starring william powell and cyd charisse . the film was directed by robert z. leonard . the film stars william powell , judy garland , and lana turner . the film was released on december 15 , 1941 , by metro-goldwyn-mayer .